{"result": {"folders": ["2018", "other", "工具使用"], "nr": 1193, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2018-04-09T02:34:05Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "data": "jfrmib71mmm6st", "type": "create", "when": "2018-04-09T02:34:05Z"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "subject": "ucore&#43;的持续集成测试", "created": "2018-04-09T02:34:05Z", "content": "<p>自动的持续集成测试可以尽早地发现不太被注意的代码修改导致的麻烦。我们的ucore&#43;经历了多个版本的自动测试。现在的做法是&#xff0c;利用外部的开源平台自动对github上的代码提交进行自动测试&#xff0c;并反馈测试结果。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>依据昨天的交流&#xff0c;现要求所有做课程设计的同学都尽可能地利用Travis CI进行自己的代码测试。目前能想到的不能自动测试的情况有两种&#xff0c;一种是依据特定硬件环境&#xff0c;一种是测试时间比较长的。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>下面是与自动测试相关的信息。供同学们参考。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Travis CI:<br /><a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/\">https://travis-ci.org/</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/travis-ci/travis-ci\">https://github.com/travis-ci/travis-ci</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>持续集成测试的例子&#xff1a;<br /><a href=\"https://github.com/oscourse-tsinghua/ucore_plus\">https://github.com/oscourse-tsinghua/ucore_plus</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/oscourse-tsinghua/ucore_plus/blob/master/.travis.yml\">https://github.com/oscourse-tsinghua/ucore_plus/blob/master/.travis.yml</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>我记得谭思楠当时写过一个自动测试的部署帮助。但我没有找到了。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>如有任何问题&#xff0c;可回复本帖进行讨论。</p>"}], "type": "note", "tags": ["2018", "instructor-note", "other", "工具使用"], "tag_good": [], "unique_views": 111, "children": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "id": "jfrmib6xtbe6ss", "config": {}, "status": "active", "drafts": null, "request_instructor": 0, "request_instructor_me": false, "bookmarked": 1, "num_favorites": 0, "my_favorite": false, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "q_edits": [], "i_edits": [], "s_edits": [], "t": 1643169360742, "default_anonymity": "no"}, "error": null, "aid": "kyv0m15y73l3xe"}